trans-unit.source: Provides information to the parser during design time.
trans-unit.target: 在设计时，请对分析器中提供的信息。

trans-unit.source: The DesignTimeParseData class is used to provide design-time parameters for several methods in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DesignTimeTemplateParser> class, which parses a template into a set of controls.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeParseData 类用于为中的多个方法提供设计时参数<xref:System.Web.UI.DesignTimeTemplateParser>类，该类将模板分析为一组控件。</xref:System.Web.UI.DesignTimeTemplateParser>
